The files in this directory come from the Istio distribution, we make some minor (significant) changes during installation

- istio-auth.yaml
  This is the standard file, we will replace image names during installation depending on the options chosen

- istio-sidecar-injector
  This is the standard file, we will replace image names during installation depending on the options chosen

- istio-sidecar-injector-configmap-release
  This is the standard file, we will replace image names during installation depending on the options chosen.  We will also switch the default policy from enabled to disabled.